"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-team-usa-hannah-roberts-explains-bmx-freestyle-at-the-2024-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"In Tokyo, U.S. riderHannah Robertsentered the competition as the favorite and the defending world champion as BMX freestyle made its Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8390908411963903, \"rank\": 0.18551707512703622, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 110, \"end\": 123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freestyle_BMX\", \"score\": 0.9999999997694431, \"rank\": 2.305708385921345e-10, \"text\": \"BMX freestyle\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freestyle_BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freestyle_BMX\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"U.S. riderHannah\", \"from\": 10, \"to\": 26}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 42, \"to\": 57}, {\"ngram\": \"the defending world champion\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 106}, {\"ngram\": \"its Olympic debut\", \"from\": 129, \"to\": 146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roberts was edged for gold by less than a point and a half, instead bringing home a silver medal.\\u00c2 The 22-year-old added back-to-back world titles to her collection following Tokyo for a total of five since 2017.\", \"from\": 148, \"to\": 361, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 324, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8390908411963903, \"rank\": 0.18551707512703622, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roberts\", \"from\": 148, \"to\": 155}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 170, \"to\": 174}, {\"ngram\": \"less than a point\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 195}, {\"ngram\": \"a half\", \"from\": 200, \"to\": 206}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 244}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"back\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 281}, {\"ngram\": \"her collection\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"a total\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once again, she enters Olympic competition as the favorite for gold.\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic competition\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"the favorite\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 420}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two-time Olympian breaks down how she puts together a run and what fans can look forward to in the BMX freestyle competition this week in Paris.\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 444, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999996094264442, \"rank\": 3.665972502088786e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freestyle_BMX\", \"score\": 0.9999999997694431, \"rank\": 2.305708385921345e-10, \"text\": \"BMX freestyle\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freestyle_BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freestyle_BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999988621994, \"rank\": 1.1377935656276347e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a run\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 492}, {\"ngram\": \"what fans\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI think the coolest thing that we are gonna see is just like the progression level change from what 2021 was to 2024,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Roberts says.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the coolest thing\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"the progression level change\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"Roberts\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSo people who watched in 2021, they are going to get an even bigger and cooler show this year, which is super exciting.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Athletes have the freedom to put down as creative and unique a run as they can in 60 seconds.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"an even bigger and cooler show\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"super exciting.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Athletes\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"the freedom\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"a run\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"60 seconds\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That creativity, which is one of the criteria the judges look at, can come in the form taking different lines, different obstacles (like box jumps or the spine) and different tricks.\\u00c2 The approach:Once she figures out how the course will best work for her, Roberts starts determining which tricks she wants to do.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That creativity\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"the criteria\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"the form\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"different lines\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1049}, {\"ngram\": \"different obstacles\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"box jumps\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"the spine\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"different tricks\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"The approach\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"Roberts\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"which tricks\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes, that goes to a conversation with her coach, who will reign her back in to a realistic run.\\u00c2 The first 45 seconds of a run are where Roberts focuses on the big tricks.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a conversation\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"a realistic run\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"The first 45 seconds\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"a run\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"Roberts\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"the big tricks\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She likes to show off the progress she has made from contest to contest and do \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cas many tricks that I have learned, or that I know how to do as possible.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The last 15 seconds requires a different approach.\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the progress\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"contest\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"many tricks\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"possible.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"The last 15 seconds\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1612}, {\"ngram\": \"a different approach\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Your legs are shot,\\\" Roberts says.\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your legs\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"Roberts\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You are like 'oh my gosh, this is brutal.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's where she adds a simple trick to gain as many points as she can without taking any unnecessary risks.\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a simple trick\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1761}, {\"ngram\": \"as many points\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"any unnecessary risks\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roberts also prefers having a back-up plan in case a trick doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t go to plan and leaves her facing in the wrong direction.\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roberts\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1841}, {\"ngram\": \"a back-up plan\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"case\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"a trick\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1892}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrong direction\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike back flips, where the rider's momentum is already taking her backwards, the approach to a front flip is different.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"back flips\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"the rider's momentum\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2006}, {\"ngram\": \"the approach\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"a front flip\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have to stop all of your momentum and throw every bit of weight and force forward,\\\" she says.\\u00c2 Flipping forward also creates a blind landing where the athlete is not able to spot the ground before the bike hits it.\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your momentum\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2121}, {\"ngram\": \"every bit\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"weight\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"a blind landing\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2228}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roberts opts to close her eyes when flipping forward.\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roberts\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2311}, {\"ngram\": \"her eyes\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI do not want to see if I landed it, and I do not want to see what a fall is going to look like,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Roberts says.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d So I just pull forward as hard as possible, and I have my eyes closed.\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fall\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"my eyes\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If my tires hit the ground, sick, but I do not know, I can not see anything.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d It's skill that Roberts says could be seen in back flips, in 360s, multiple in the air or in oppo--where the trick goes in the opposite direction than the rider usually does it.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my tires\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2575}, {\"ngram\": \"skill\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2639}, {\"ngram\": \"Roberts\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2652}, {\"ngram\": \"back flips\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2685}, {\"ngram\": \"360s\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"oppo\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2726}, {\"ngram\": \"the trick\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2743}, {\"ngram\": \"the opposite direction\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"the rider\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You go up the ramp and your hands stay on the bars and your bars always stay straight, but the entire rest of your bike will go completely around.\\\"\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ramp\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2828}, {\"ngram\": \"your hands\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2843}, {\"ngram\": \"the bars\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"your bars\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2874}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire rest\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2916}, {\"ngram\": \"your bike\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 2985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Loading recommendations\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 2982}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations \\u00c2\\u00a9 2026ABG-SI LLC-SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3129, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"personalized content recommendations\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\\u00a9 2026ABG-SI LLC-SPORTS ILLUSTRATED\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3085}, {\"ngram\": \"A REGISTERED TRADEMARK\", \"from\": 3089, \"to\": 3111}, {\"ngram\": \"ABG-SI LLC\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All Rights\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The content\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3164}, {\"ngram\": \"this site\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3177}, {\"ngram\": \"entertainment and educational purposes\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for i